React frontend for access on web (Firebase)
- password protected (authentification)
- view all info on searchable table

Backend server hosted on Firebase?
API:
GET   /:group/all   => Return information for everyone
GET   /:group/:id   => Return information for that person
POST  /:group      => Add information for new person
PATCH /:group/:id   => Update information for person
PATCH /:group/all   => Update for all updates

Database schema:
Last updated timestamp
First name
last name
age
weight
height
blood pressure: int
current meds: list of strings
symptoms: list of strings

web/public: Express JS
web/public/client: React JS
